data.message: got no where to go with my rhymes so im gonna lay it down here... bitch im dissertated but im elevated from these silly plots that you contemplated my number one dream is to be educated only to perfect these intricate rhymes that are laid before me. im on a roll but not on the honor roll because im dyslexic and my a's are actually c's i know you haters wanna see me fall but if i ever do you can bet that ill bounce back like lamar when he gets passed an 8 ball you want to hate me well fine but your just mad that i put the y in ours and made the world yours hence mine theres no time to crack under pressure especially when your ass is on the line you people need to check the skill and realize whats real these rappers aren't built on self perfection they just throw a trendy beat in your direction just to pass inspection when all they do is come up with a few rhymes then suddenly get added to the top of the list of written by. so get ready for my untold chapter evil is live backwards and if you add d to evil you got the devil so i guess im one hellish rapper i was born hurt and cursed therefor grew up with a torn mind that made me blurt a curse.... thanks eminem for helping me find something that  i can put my mind to and be somewhat decent at it
